  "detailed_description": "Speed Run is a first person platform video game, each level is full of traps, obstacles and fatal falls that you must avoid at all costs. Each level has its unique theme with different music and environments.<br> The objective of the game is that you can complete the levels as quickly as possible and without dying, since dying penalizes you by starting the level from the beginning.<br>This game updates regularly with new levels and characters!<br>When new levels arrive, they will be added as FREE updates. No DLC or micro transactions of any kind!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028700/extras/4b4094f837c8b338072a62e57a41dff7.poster.avif?t=1763934307\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028700/extras/4b4094f837c8b338072a62e57a41dff7.webm?t=1763934307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028700/extras/4b4094f837c8b338072a62e57a41dff7.mp4?t=1763934307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Speed Run is a first person platform video game, each level is full of traps, obstacles and fatal falls that you must avoid at all costs. Each level has its unique theme with different music and environments.<br> The objective of the game is that you can complete the levels as quickly as possible and without dying, since dying penalizes you by starting the level from the beginning.<br>This game updates regularly with new levels and characters!<br>When new levels arrive, they will be added as FREE updates. No DLC or micro transactions of any kind!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028700/extras/4b4094f837c8b338072a62e57a41dff7.poster.avif?t=1763934307\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028700/extras/4b4094f837c8b338072a62e57a41dff7.webm?t=1763934307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028700/extras/4b4094f837c8b338072a62e57a41dff7.mp4?t=1763934307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
